      <talk_answer link_index="n1757_academic-2-c" mid="48" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Comelina$<BR>I'm sorry but I eavesdropped on what you were saying just now. Maybe I can help you.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Comelina presses the buttons on her small device)</FONT> Traitor in the Brotherhood of Steel?</html>]]></talk_question>
